      "title": "Three-wheeler driver hacked to death in Katunayake",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A 38-year-old three-wheeler driver was murdered at Heenatiyana area Mahagama, Katunayake on Sunday (17) night.",
        "Sri Lanka Police said that the murder took place when the victim was on his way to a filling station to obtain fuel.",
        "According to the Police, a group had arrived in another three-wheeler attacked the victim with swords, and carried out the murder last night.",
        "The Police further said that the murder had taken place due to a personal dispute and the suspects are yet to be identified."
      ],
